a.title: Triggered
a.notes: A trap can only be set as triggered (value 2) IFF the trap has been set (value 1). A sensor input is the only way  to trigger the sensor. All other channel values are set by the client. A yabby must have a reason value of 46 for the device to be considered a trigger. All other reasons will not fire a trigger.
